<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Heritage and Culture Page</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #333;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .navbar nav ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .navbar nav ul li {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .navbar nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url('<%= result[0].imageUrl[0] %>');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            padding: 50px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .about-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .about-content {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            max-width: 500px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 2;
        }

        .about-text h3 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .about-text h4 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
            color: #444;
        }

        .about-text p,
        .about-text ul {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .about-text ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }


        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .view {
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* Explore Section */
        .explore {
            padding: 50px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .explore h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .site-container,
        .culture-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .site-card,
        .culture-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 22%;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            display: block;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .explore-text {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }

        .site-card img,
        .culture-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .card-content {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .card-content h3 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .card-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #777;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .site-card:hover,
        .culture-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media (max-width: 1200px) {
            .about-content {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .about-content.image-left,
            .about-content.image-right {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .about-text,
            .about-image {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .about-text {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) {

            .site-card,
            .culture-card {
                width: 45%;
            }

            .pinmap,
            .view {
                height: 60vh;
                /* Adjusted height for medium screens */
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {

            .site-card,
            .culture-card {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .btn-primary {
                padding: 8px 16px;
            }

            .about-text h3 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .about-text h4 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .about-text p,
            .about-text ul {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .pinmap,
            .view {
                height: 50vh;
                /* Adjusted height for smaller screens */
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .btn-primary {
                padding: 6px 12px;
            }

            .about-text h3 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .about-text h4 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .about-text p,
            .about-text ul {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .pinmap,
            .view {
                height: 40vh;
                /* Adjusted height for the smallest screens */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="logo"><img src="/img/logo.svg" alt="Taj Mahal"></div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/explore">Explore</a></li>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Discover the Culture</h1>
            <p>Explore the rich culture.</p>
            <a href="#cultures" class="btn-primary">Explore more</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="cultures">
        <h2 class="explore-text">Explore Cultures</h2>
    </section>


    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
        <!-- First Half -->
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="<%= result[0].imageUrl[1] %>" alt="Taj Mahal">
            </div>
            <div class="about-text">
                <h3>
                    <%= result[0].name %>
                </h3>
                <h4>Overview</h4>
                <p>
                    <%= result[0].overview %>
                </p>
                <h4>History</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Origins:</strong>
                        <%= result[0].history.origin %>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Significance: </strong>
                        <%= result[0].history.significance %>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Second Half -->
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h4>Celebration Type</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Lighting of Diyas: </strong>
                        <%= result[0].celebrationType[0] %>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Fireworks and Festivities:</strong>
                        <%=result[0].celebrationType[1] %>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Pujas and Offerings:</strong>
                        <%=result[0].celebrationType[2] %>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h4>Popular places</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>
                            <%=result[0].popularPlace[0] %>
                        </strong></li>
                    <li><strong>
                            <%=result[0].popularPlace[1] %>
                        </strong></li>
                    <li><strong>
                            <%=result[0].popularPlace[2] %>
                        </strong></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="<%= result[0].imageUrl[2] %>" alt="Taj Mahal">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!--cultures-->
    <section id="cultures">
        <h2 class="explore-text">Explore Cultures</h2>
        <div class="culture-container">
            <a href="/explore/culture/66d839d69e12dd4b14766096" class="culture-card">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dv2wvvbbz/image/upload/v1725440140/rakshabhandhan1_qe6ql1.jpg" alt="Bharatanatyam">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Raksha Bandhan</h3>
                    <p>Raksha Bandhan is a heartwarming festival celebrating the bond between brothers and sisters.</p>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/explore/culture/66d839d69e12dd4b14766092" class="culture-card">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dv2wvvbbz/image/upload/v1725440136/durga3_azzj3j.jpg" alt="Rangoli">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Navratri</h3>
                    <p>Navratri is a vibrant and spiritually significant Hindu festival dedicated to the worship of Goddess Durga.</p>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/explore/culture/66d839d69e12dd4b14766090" class="culture-card">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dv2wvvbbz/image/upload/v1725440135/diwali_1_rpitoc.jpg" alt="Kathakali">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Diwali</h3>
                    <p>Diwali, also known as Deepavali, is one of the most significant and widely celebrated festivals in India.</p>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/explore/culture/66d839d69e12dd4b14766098" class="culture-card">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dv2wvvbbz/image/upload/v1725440136/eid1_gfhgmo.jpg" alt="Bihu Dance">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Eid al-Fitr</h3>
                    <p>Eid al-Fitr, also known as the Festival of Breaking the Fast, marks the end of Ramadan, the Islamic holy month of fasting.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Explore Section -->
    <section id="heritage-sites">
        <h2 class="explore-text">Explore Heritage Sites</h2>
        <div class="site-container">
            <a href="/explore/site/66dcb11d3099edd7c9e1a592" class="site-card">
                <img src="/img/taj1.jpg" alt="Taj Mahal">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Taj Mahal</h3>
                    <p>An iconic symbol of love and one of the Seven Wonders of the World.</p>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/explore/site/66dcb11d3099edd7c9e1a594" class="site-card">
                <img src="/img/qutub.jpg" alt="Qutub Minar">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Qutub Minar</h3>
                    <p>The tallest brick minaret in the world, showcasing Indo-Islamic architecture.</p>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/explore/site/66dcb11d3099edd7c9e1a596" class="site-card">
                <img src="/img/sun.jpg" alt="Sun Temple">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Sun Temple, Konark</h3>
                    <p>A 13th-century temple dedicated to the Sun God, a UNESCO World Heritage Site.</p>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/explore/site/66dcb11d3099edd7c9e1a599" class="site-card">
                <img src="/img/humpi.jpg" alt="Hampi">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Hampi</h3>
                    <p>An ancient village with ruins of temples and palaces, a UNESCO World Heritage Site.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <section>
        <footer class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 Heritage and Culture. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </section>
    <script src="/js/show.js"></script>
</body>

</html>